---
layout: base.njk
title: Other Rabbit-Friendly Organizations
description: "Florida organizations that rescue or care for rabbits alongside other animals."
value_index: 2
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <h1>Other Rabbit-Friendly Organizations</h1>
  <p>{{ directory.excluded_organizations | length }} Florida organizations that rescue or care for rabbits alongside other animals.</p>
  {% set v = directory.shared_values.values[value_index] %}<p class="hero-epigraph"><a href="/values/#{{ v.statement | slugify }}">{{ v.statement }}</a></p>
</section>

<div class="other-rescues-intro">
  <p>These organizations were reviewed but not included in the <a href="/directory/">main directory</a>, typically because their primary focus extends beyond rabbits. They may still have rabbits available for adoption, and we encourage you to reach out to them directly.</p>
</div>

<div class="mini-card-grid">
  {%- for org in directory.excluded_organizations | sortByName %}
  <div class="mini-card">
    <h2 class="mini-card-name" id="{{ org.name | slugify }}">{{ org.name }}</h2>
    <p class="mini-card-desc">{{ org.reason }}</p>
    {%- if org.url %}
    <a class="mini-card-link" href="{{ org.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ org.url | replace("https://www.", "") | replace("https://", "") | trimTrailingSlash }} ↗</a>
    {%- endif %}
  </div>
  {%- endfor %}
</div>

<div class="other-rescues-footer">
  <div class="correction-cta">
    <p>Is your organization missing or incorrect?</p>
    <a class="btn-primary" href="/contact/">Submit a Correction &#8594;</a>
  </div>
</div>
